text: E.A. — Extraordinary Accident () is a 1958 Soviet drama movie directed by Viktor Ivchenko.ЧП — ЧРЕЗВЫЧАЙНОЕ ПРОИСШЕСТВИЕЖенщина советского лейтенанта It stars Mikhail Kuznetsov, Alexander Anurov, and Vyacheslav Tikhonov. ==Actors== *Mikhail Kuznetsov — Anton Kovalenko *Alexander Anurov — Leonid Kalugin *Vyacheslav Tikhonov — Victor Rayskiy *Taisiya Litvinenko — Rita Voronkovа *Anatoly Solovyov Grachev *Giuli Chokhonelidze — Javakheti *Dmitri Kapka — Kharitonenko == References == ==Other websites== * Category:1958 drama movies Category:Soviet drama movies Category:Movies directed by Viktor Ivchenko
